data.name: lblBatchHelp.Text
data.value: • 1 page: Send exactly 1 PDF page in each request. GPT processes pages one by one. • 2 pages: Send 2 PDF pages together in a single request. GPT can read both pages at once. • 3 pages: Send 3 PDF pages together so GPT sees more context. • 4 pages: Send 4 PDF pages together for maximum context.
